This is a basic example used for testing Verilator/GTKwave.

More information on the open source tools demonstrated in this example:

  Verilator: https://www.veripool.org/wiki/verilator
  GTKWave: http://gtkwave.sourceforge.net

The example with set-up was taken from:
  http://rattus-pubis.blogspot.no/2011/02/experimenting-with-verilator-counter.html